---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="About Me"
	description="Learn more about my background, skills, and approach to web development"
>
	<div class="section-container">
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
			<!-- Main Content -->
			<div class="md:col-span-8">
				<h1 class="heading-xl">About Me</h1>
				
				<div class="prose">
					<p class="paragraph">
						Hello! I'm [Your Name], a passionate web developer focused on crafting clean, user-friendly websites and applications. With a strong foundation in modern web technologies and a keen eye for design, I strive to create digital experiences that are both beautiful and functional.
					</p>
					
					<h2 class="heading-lg mt-8">My Journey</h2>
					<p class="paragraph">
						My interest in web development started back in 2012 when I decided to try editing custom Tumblr themes â€” turns out hacking together a custom reblog button taught me a lot about HTML & CSS! Since then, I've been continuously learning and evolving my skills to keep up with the rapidly changing landscape of web development.
					</p>
					
					<p class="paragraph">
						Fast-forward to today, and I've had the privilege of working at a software agency, a large corporation, and a start-up. My main focus these days is building accessible, inclusive products and digital experiences for a variety of clients.
					</p>
					
					<h2 class="heading-lg mt-8">My Approach</h2>
					<p class="paragraph">
						I believe in the power of simplicity. My approach to development emphasizes clean code, intuitive user interfaces, and accessible design. Every project I undertake is built with a focus on performance, scalability, and maintainability.
					</p>
					
					<p class="paragraph">
						I'm passionate about creating websites that not only look great but also perform exceptionally well. This means paying close attention to accessibility, responsiveness, and user experience across all devices and platforms.
					</p>
					
					<h2 class="heading-lg mt-8">When I'm Not Coding</h2>
					<p class="paragraph">
						When I'm not in front of a computer screen, I enjoy hiking in the mountains, experimenting with new cooking recipes, and playing the guitar. I find that maintaining diverse interests helps me stay creative and bring fresh perspectives to my technical work.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="mt-12">
					<a href="/contact" class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center">
						Get In Touch
						<Icon name="ph:arrow-right" class="ml-2 w-4 h-4" />
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Sidebar -->
			<div class="md:col-span-4">
				<div class="card-modern sticky top-24">
					<div class="aspect-square rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-6">
						<img src="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg" alt="Profile Photo" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
					</div>
					
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Skills & Expertise</h3>
					
					<div class="space-y-3">
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-text-secondary font-medium mb-2">Frontend</h4>
							<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">HTML</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">CSS</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">JavaScript</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">React</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">Astro</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-text-secondary font-medium mb-2">Backend</h4>
							<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">Node.js</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">Express</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">MongoDB</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">GraphQL</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-text-secondary font-medium mb-2">Tools</h4>
							<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">Git</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">Figma</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded bg-primary-bg border border-primary text-primary font-mono">VS Code</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					<div class="mt-8">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Let's Connect</h3>
						<div class="flex gap-3">
							<a href="https://github.com/yourusername" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
								class="bg-primary-bg p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:bg-opacity-20 transition-colors">
								<Icon name="ph:github-logo-duotone" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
							</a>
							<a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
								class="bg-primary-bg p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:bg-opacity-20 transition-colors">
								<Icon name="ph:linkedin-logo-duotone" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
							</a>
							<a href="https://twitter.com/yourusername" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
								class="bg-primary-bg p-2 rounded-full hover:bg-primary hover:bg-opacity-20 transition-colors">
								<Icon name="ph:twitter-logo-duotone" class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" />
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
